Class Coord

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Coord

  • public class Coord
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a coordinate on the game board. Stores a integer (x,y) game position, and allows it to be updated, or retrieved.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
